                    </form>
                <% } %>
            </nav>
        </header>

        <main id="hero">
            <h2>HyperSupportDesk - QuickFixes</h2>
            <ol id="quickfixes">
                <li>Computer won't turn on
                <ul>
                    <li>- Make sure computer is plugged in.</li>
                    <li>- Make sure monitor is plugged in to computer and to a power outlet.</li>
                    <li>- Hold down power button.</li>
                    <li>- Unplug from power outlet and press power button to discharge the device.</li>
                    <li>- let charge for 30-60 minutes.</li>
                </ul></li>

                <li>Computer is running slow
                <ul>
                    <li>- Reboot computer.</li>
                    <li>- Close some Chrome tabs or unneeded apps.</li>
                    <li>- Run "Disk Cleanup".</li>
                </ul></li>
                
                <li>Can't acces the internet
                <ul>
                    <li>- Make sure the ethernet cable in plugged in if it is a desktop.</li>
                    <li>- Disconnect from the network and reconnect.</li>
                    <li>- Reboot the device.</li>
                    <li>- The site may be down, try again in 30 minutes.</li>
                </ul></li>

                <li>Mouse is not working
                <ul>
                    <li>- If it is wireless, turn it off then back on.</li>
                    <li>- If it is wireless, Change out batteries.</li>
                    <li>- If it is wired, make sure it is plugged in.</li>
                    <li>- Get a brand new mouse.</li>
                </ul></li>

                <li>There is no audio
                <ul>
                    <li>- Make sure the video or tab isn't muted.</li>
                    <li>- Select the speaker icon in the bottom right corner of the screen and make sure it is high enough to hear.</li>
                    <li>- Select a different option under the speaker icon.</li>
                    <li>- Make sure you don't have headphone connected to the device.</li>
                    <li>- Restart the device.</li>
                </ul></li>
            </ol>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>

</html>